Done! I've set up **6 persistent rules** that hide all video recommendations across the page:

- **`#related`** — the entire recommendations sidebar on watch pages
- **`ytd-watch-next-secondary-results-renderer`** — the "Up next" / related videos list
- **`.ytp-fullscreen-grid`** — end-screen video suggestions shown inside the player
- **`ytd-shelf-renderer`** — trending/recommended video shelves on browse/home pages
- **`ytd-grid-video-renderer`** — individual video cards in grid layouts
- **`yt-lockup-view-model`** — the modern card format used for recommended videos

These rules will persist across page loads so you won't see any video recommendations going forward.
